V3:
 - use get_format to select AV_PIX_FMT_DRM_PRIME
 - use hw_configs
 - add handling of AV_PIX_FMT_YUV420P format (for raspberry pi)
 - add handling of AV_PIX_FMT_YUYV422 format (for i.MX6 coda decoder)

